Cheshire, England":"英國英格蘭爾馬爾帕斯","lifeSummary":"當William Patric於大約1190年出生在英國英格蘭爾馬爾帕斯時，他的父親William Robert de Patrick36歲，母親Mrs. Robert Patric20歲。他於大約1200年與Mrs. William Patric在英國英格蘭爾馬爾帕斯結婚。他們至少是1個兒子的父母。他去世於1230年之後。"},"zh-hans":{"Abt 1190–Aft 1230":"大约1190年–1230年之后","1190–1230":"1190年–1230年","1192–Male":"1192年–殁","1200–Male":"1200年–殁","1192–Female":"1192年–殁","1203–Male":"1203年–殁","1203–1230":"1203年–1230年","1155–1200":"1155年–1200年","1172–Female":"1172年–殁","1190":"1190年","1203":"1203年","Aft 1200":"1200年之后","1200":"1200年","1155":"1155年","1230":"1230年","about 1200":"大约1200年","Aft 1230":"1230年之后","1172":"1172年","1192":"1192年","Abt 1190":"大约1190年","Malpas, Cheshire,, England":"英国英格兰爾馬爾帕斯","of Malpas, Cheshire, England":"英国英格兰爾馬爾帕斯","Of Malpas, Cheshire, England":"英国英格兰爾馬爾帕斯","lifeSummary":"当William Patric于大约1190年出生在英国英格兰爾馬爾帕斯时，他的父亲William Robert de Patrick36岁，母亲Mrs. Robert Patric20岁。他于大约1200年与Mrs. William Patric在英国英格兰爾馬爾帕斯结婚。他们至少是1个儿子的父母。他去世于1230年之后。"},"hr":{"Abt 1190–Aft 1230":"oko 1190.–nakon 1230.","1190–1230":"1190–1230","1192–Male":"1192–preminuo","1200–Male":"1200–preminuo","1192–Female":"1192–preminula","1203–Male":"1203.–preminuo","1203–1230":"1203.–1230","1155–1200":"1155–1200","1172–Female":"1172–preminula","1190":"1190","1203":"1203.","Aft 1200":"nakon 1200.","1200":"1200","1155":"1155","1230":"1230","about 1200":"oko 1200.","Aft 1230":"nakon 1230.","1172":"1172","1192":"1192","Abt 1190":"oko 1190.","Malpas, Cheshire,, England":"Malpas, Cheshire, Engleska, United Kingdom","of Malpas, Cheshire, England":"Malpas, Cheshire, Engleska, United Kingdom","Of Malpas, Cheshire, England":"Malpas, Cheshire, Engleska, United Kingdom"},"cs":{"Abt 1190–Aft 1230":"okolo 1190–po 1230","1190–1230":"1190–1230","1192–Male":"1192–Zesnulý","1200–Male":"1200–Zesnulý","1192–Female":"1192–Zesnulá","1203–Male":"1203–Zesnulý","1203–1230":"1203–1230","1155–1200":"1155–1200","1172–Female":"1172–Zesnulá","1190":"1190","1203":"1203","Aft 1200":"po 1200","1200":"1200","1155":"1155","1230":"1230","